  1→//axhob_operation
  2→{rbtgo_director_create}
  3→
  4→The
  5→{rbtr_governor}
  6→creates a
  7→{rbtr_director}
  8→{giam_service_account}
  9→with build management permissions:
 10→
 11→//axhoq_precondition
 12→* Execute {rbtoe_check_rubric_repo_url} using {rbtr_governor} RBRA credentials
 13→
 14→//axhoq_precondition
 15→* Execute {rbtoe_check_cbv2_connection} to verify {rbtgi_cbv2_connection} is active
 16→
 17→//axhop_parameter_from_type
 18→{rbtr_director}
 19→. *Validate Input Parameters*:
 20→.. {rbbc_require}
 21→`«INPUT_INSTANCE»` provided as first argument
 22→.. {rbbc_store}
 23→`«DIRECTOR_ACCOUNT_NAME»` as `rb-director-«INPUT_INSTANCE»`
 24→.. {rbbc_store}
 25→`«DIRECTOR_EMAIL»` as `«DIRECTOR_ACCOUNT_NAME»@{rbrr_depot_project_id}.iam.gserviceaccount.com`
 26→
 27→//axhoq_precondition
 28→* {rbbc_require}
 29→`BURD_OUTPUT_DIR` environment variable set and directory exists
 30→
 31→//axhos_step
 32→. *Authenticate as
 33→{rbtr_governor}*:
 34→.. Execute
 35→{rbtoe_governor_authenticate}
 36→.. {rbbc_store}
 37→`«GOVERNOR_TOKEN»` for subsequent API calls
 38→
 39→//axhos_step
 40→. *Create
 41→{rbtr_director}
 42→Service Account*:
 43→.. {rbbc_call}
 44→link:https://cloud.google.com/iam/docs/reference/rest/v1/projects.serviceAccounts/create[iam.serviceAccounts.create] with:
 45→... accountId: `«DIRECTOR_ACCOUNT_NAME»`
 46→... displayName: `Recipe Bottle Director («INPUT_INSTANCE»)`
 47→... description: `Create/destroy container images for «INPUT_INSTANCE»`
 48→... project:
 49→{rbrr_depot_project_id}
 50→.. {rbbc_require}
 51→HTTP 200 response
 52→.. {rbbc_store}
 53→`«DIRECTOR_UNIQUE_ID»` from response `.uniqueId` field
 54→
 55→//axhos_step
 56→. *Verify Service Account Creation*:
 57→.. {rbbc_call}
 58→link:https://cloud.google.com/iam/docs/reference/rest/v1/projects.serviceAccounts/get[iam.serviceAccounts.get] for `projects/-/serviceAccounts/«DIRECTOR_UNIQUE_ID»`
 59→.. NOTE: Numeric ID is valid in API URL paths (immediately resolvable). Not valid in IAM policy `members` — see RBS0 IAM Member Format.
 60→.. {rbbc_require}
 61→service account accessible
 62→
 63→//axhos_step
 64→. *Preflight: Ensure Pristine Key State*:
 65→.. {rbbc_call}
 66→link:https://cloud.google.com/iam/docs/reference/rest/v1/projects.serviceAccounts.keys/list[serviceAccounts.keys.list] for `«DIRECTOR_EMAIL»`
 67→.. {rbbc_store}
 68→`«EXISTING_KEYS»` from response `.keys[]`
 69→.. {rbbc_require}
 70→no keys with `keyType: USER_MANAGED` exist
 71→.. {rbbc_fatal}
 72→if USER_MANAGED keys found: "Manual cleanup required via Console"
 73→
 74→//axhos_step
 75→. *Generate Service Account Key*:
 76→.. {rbbc_call}
 77→link:https://cloud.google.com/iam/docs/reference/rest/v1/projects.serviceAccounts.keys/create[serviceAccounts.keys.create] for `«DIRECTOR_EMAIL»` with:
 78→... privateKeyType: `TYPE_GOOGLE_CREDENTIALS_FILE`
 79→.. {rbbc_store}
 80→`«DIRECTOR_PRIVATE_KEY_DATA»` from response `.privateKeyData` field
 81→.. {rbtoe_rbra_generate}
 82→converts `«DIRECTOR_PRIVATE_KEY_DATA»` to `«DIRECTOR_RBRA_FILE»`
 83→
 84→//axhos_step
 85→. *Get Depot Project Number*:
 86→.. {rbbc_call}
 87→link:https://cloud.google.com/resource-manager/reference/rest/v3/projects/get[projects.get] for
 88→{rbrr_depot_project_id}
 89→.. {rbbc_store}
 90→`«PROJECT_NUMBER»` from `.projectNumber` field
 91→
 92→//axhos_step
 93→. *Grant Project-Level Permissions*:
 94→.. {rbbc_call}
 95→link:https://cloud.google.com/resource-manager/reference/rest/v3/projects/setIamPolicy[projects.setIamPolicy] for
 96→{rbrr_depot_project_id}
 97→.. Add `serviceAccount:«DIRECTOR_EMAIL»` with roles:
 98→... `roles/cloudbuild.builds.editor` (submit and manage builds)
 99→... `roles/viewer` (read project resources)
100→... `roles/cloudbuild.connectionAdmin` (CB v2 connection and repository management)
101→.. Policy version: 3
102→.. {rbbc_require}
103→IAM policy update successful
104→
105→//axhos_step
106→. *Grant Secret Manager Access for Inscribe*:
107→.. NOTE:
108→{rbtr_director}
109→needs to fetch the GitHub PAT from Secret Manager during
110→{rbtgo_rubric_inscribe}
111→to construct authenticated git URLs.
112→.. {rbbc_call}
113→link:https://cloud.google.com/secret-manager/docs/reference/rest/v1/projects.secrets/setIamPolicy[secrets.setIamPolicy] for `projects/{rbrr_depot_project_id}/secrets/RBGC_CBV2_PAT_SECRET_NAME`
114→.. Add `serviceAccount:«DIRECTOR_EMAIL»` with `roles/secretmanager.secretAccessor`
115→.. {rbbc_require}
116→IAM binding successful
117→
118→//axhos_step
119→. *Grant
120→{rbtr_mason}
121→Impersonation*:
122→.. NOTE:
123→{rbtr_director}
124→submits builds that execute as
125→{rbtr_mason}.
126→This requires `serviceAccountUser` permission on
127→{rbtr_mason}.
128→.. {rbbc_call}
129→link:https://cloud.google.com/iam/docs/reference/rest/v1/projects.serviceAccounts/setIamPolicy[serviceAccounts.setIamPolicy] for
130→{rbtr_mason}
131→service account
132→.. Add `serviceAccount:«DIRECTOR_EMAIL»` with `roles/iam.serviceAccountUser`
133→.. {rbbc_require}
134→IAM binding successful
135→
136→//axhos_step
137→. *Grant
138→{rbtgi_build_bucket}
139→Access*:
140→.. {rbbc_call}
141→link:https://cloud.google.com/storage/docs/json_api/v1/buckets/setIamPolicy[buckets.setIamPolicy] for
142→{rbtgi_build_bucket}
143→.. Add `serviceAccount:«DIRECTOR_EMAIL»` with roles:
144→... `roles/storage.objectCreator` (upload sources)
145→... `roles/storage.objectViewer` (verify uploads)
146→.. {rbbc_require}
147→bucket IAM update successful
148→
149→//axhos_step
150→. *Grant
151→{rbtgi_repository}
152→Admin Access*:
153→.. {rbbc_call}
154→link:https://cloud.google.com/artifact-registry/docs/reference/rest/v1/projects.locations.repositories/setIamPolicy[repositories.setIamPolicy] for
155→{rbtgi_repository}
156→.. Add `serviceAccount:«DIRECTOR_EMAIL»` with `roles/artifactregistry.repoAdmin`
157→.. {rbbc_require}
158→repository IAM update successful
159→
160→//axhoo_output_of_type
161→{rbtgi_rbra_file}
162→. *Display Installation Instructions*:
163→.. {rbbc_show}
164→Director created successfully
165→.. {rbbc_show}
166→RBRA file location: `«DIRECTOR_RBRA_FILE»`
167→.. {rbbc_show}
168→installation command:
169→... `cp "«DIRECTOR_RBRA_FILE»" "{rbrr_director_rbra_file}"`
170→.. {rbbc_warn}
171→if
172→{rbrr_director_rbra_file}
173→already exists
174→
175→//axhoc_completion
176→Successful execution creates director service account.
177→
